Description: The Intersection of Food and FunWith its vibrant retro design, Avenue Caf‚ puts a glamorous twist on old school Vegas. Slide into a high-backed booth for a hearty breakfast of a made-to-order omelet and a signature mimosa. Or linger a little longer over a sandwich or burger at lunch.
